<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>New user <%= SiteName %></title>
    <!-- Bootstrap -->
    <link href="<%=StyleSheet%>" rel="stylesheet">

    <%=Favicon%>

    <!-- jQuery (necessary for Bootstrap's JavaScript plugins) -->
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.11.2/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <!-- Latest compiled and minified JavaScript -->
    <script src="js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    <!-- Enable tooltips for this page -->
    <script type="text/javascript">
        $(function () {
          $('[data-toggle="tooltip"]').tooltip()
      })
    </script>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class=".col-md-8 .col-md-offset-2">
                <h1>Welcome <%= @name %></h1>
                <p>If I'm not mistaken, you're new to these parts.</p>
                <p>Please enter at least one URL of a news item you find interesting, the more you enter the better your results will be.</p>
                <p>For example if you like Formula 1 you might input <a href="http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/formula1/31409991">http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/formula1/31409991</a>; or if you're into space, something like this <a href="http://blogs.esa.int/rosetta/2015/02/16/cometwatch-14-february-flyby-special/">http://blogs.esa.int/rosetta/2015/02/16/cometwatch-14-february-flyby-special/</a>. Just copy a few URLs of blog posts or news items that tickle your fancy.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class=".col-md-6 .col-md-offset-3">
                <form class="form-horizontal" action="<%= @name %>/likeSeed" method="post">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="url0">URL</label>
                        <input type="url" class="form-control" name="url0" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <input type="url" class="form-control" name="url1">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <input type="url" class="form-control" name="url2">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <input type="url" class="form-control" name="url3">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <input type="url" class="form-control" name="url4">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Generate your stream</button>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <%=erb :'partials/footerButtons'%>
</body>